```

Now, when I PUT ```{"hasauto":{"model":"foo"}}``` I expect HTTP 400 ValidationError to be returned, with some pretty details in body. Instead I got HTTP 500 because of mongoengine.ValidationError raised at mongoengine/base/document.py in validate.

Method is_valid ignores field requirement somehow. And I cannot figure out - why?

